{"tid":1267221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫停中國「一帶一路」港口建設 坦桑尼亞斥條件剝削!!","createTime":"2019-06-29T18:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:50:06.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e04724674b7b3c8dcbf83dcf3b21219f31f3fbcd","tid":1267221,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:38:38.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】東非的坦桑尼亞以不公平條件為由，叫停中國支持的巴加莫約港口（Bagamoyo Port）建設項目，項目投資百億美元，被稱為「坦桑尼亞深圳」，包括修建連接石油氣勘探的鐵路、公路在內的一個特別經濟區，建成後將成為東非最大的門戶。該項目由中國招商局國際有限公司投資和管理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「一帶一路」近來在亞洲，非洲和中東不斷碰壁。圖為工人在斯里蘭卡可倫坡公路上施工。</strong><br />\n<br />\n2013年3月，國家主席習近平與坦桑尼亞總統基奎特（Jakaya Kikwete）簽署備忘錄，該項目在2015年舉行奠基儀式。但前總統下台後，繼任總統約翰&middot;馬古富力（John Magufuli）未將此項目列為重點。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音電台報道，馬古富力在6月14日指摘中國對此項目提出的融資條件是「剝削性的和讓人為難的」（exploitative and awkward），「他們要我們給他們33年抵押和99年租約，一旦港口運營，我們不能對誰來投資過問」。中國外交部發言人耿爽前日就此回應說：「中方支持中國企業根據市場化原則參與坦桑尼亞基礎設施建設。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20190629/s00013/1561745549330/%E5%8F%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%81%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%9D%A6%E6%A1%91%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E6%96%A5%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%89%9D%E5%89%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20190629%2Fs00013%2F1561745549330%2F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%259D%25A6%25E6%25A1%2591%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%2589%258A&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=f3077bd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20190629%2Fs00013%2F1561745549330%2F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%259D%25A6%25E6%25A1%2591%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%2589%258A&h=9efda451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20190629/s00013/1561745549330/%E5%8F%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%81%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%9D%A6%E6%A1%91%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E6%96%A5%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%89%9D%E5%89%8A</a>"},{"pid":"5d3b35e75b14f04ed04d990650c9c574ae87a751","tid":1267221,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:50:06.000Z","msg":"黑錢基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真識玩"}]}